Installation instructions:
+------------------------+

Upgrade the package as root:
# upgradepkg httpd-2.4.34-i586-1_slack14.2.txz

Then, restart Apache httpd:

# /etc/rc.d/rc.httpd stop
# /etc/rc.d/rc.httpd start


